title: Oma Marnie's Kiwi Pie Bakery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small cafe offering hot savory pies including ones with vegetable and bean fillings: mushrrom, black beans chipotle, yellow cashew curry, chickpea-mangold, etc. Pies are also available frozen to take and bake at home. Has salads, vegan sweet slices for dessert, weekly changing vegan soup, soymilk for drinks.
